 of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2590 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/09\/sadaqah-sabil-sabeel-allah-seven-hundred\/","url_meta":{"origin":24357,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Reward: Charity in the way of Allah multiplied","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Mas\u2019ud reported: A man came with a bridled camel and he said, \u201cThis is in the way of Allah.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou will have for it seven hundred camels on the Day of Resurrection; each of them will be bridled.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18139,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/17\/closest-akhirah-just-imams\/","url_meta":{"origin":24357,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Justice: Closest to Allah in Hereafter are just leaders","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most beloved of people to Allah on the Day of Resurrection and the nearest to Him will be the just leader. The most hated of people to Allah and th